fr.sorbonne_u.cps.dht_mapreduce.interfaces.content

Interface ContentKeyI

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public interface ContentKeyI
extends java.io.Serializable
    The interface ContentKeyI must be implemented by all classes that define keys to be put in the DHT

    Description

    As in any hash table, distributed hash tables store key-value pairs. As keys in a DHT will have to be transmitted through network connections, they have to be serialisable.

    Invariants

     invariant       true        // no more invariant
